rticle><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/b41b40d04cc32e3e4f904f051c19deec" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Michele-Curnis-120x150.jpg" width="80" height="100" alt="Michele Curnis" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Michele Curnis"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/michele-curnis/">View all articles by Michele Curnis</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/03/un-mondo-che-dura-un-istante-per-tornare-subito-a-dissolversi/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Un mondo che dura un istante, per tornare subito a dissolversi</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/03/new-york-metropolitan-otello/" rel="next">New York, Metropolitan: Otello <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"><h2 class="comments-title"> 2 comments</h2><ol class="commentlist"><li class="comment even thread-even depth-1" id="li-comment-16703"> <article id="comment-16703" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/7d01597824cb4fe90e3af811f7bfecfc?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">Adele Rovereto</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/03/lincubo-grottesco-di-cuore-di-cane-affascina-la-scala/#comment-16703"><time datetime="2013-03-23T18:01:06+00:00">23 marzo 2013 at 18:01</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Pur non avendo potuto assistere alla rappresentazione scaligera, la recensione di assoluta professionalit e di grande suggestione di Curnis mi ha fatto vivere l&#8217;emozione di uno straordinario spettacolo, permettendomi di coglierne la profondit artistica. Grazie!</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li><li class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1" id="li-comment-16772"> <article id="comment-16772" class="comment clearfix"> <header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard"><div class="comment-avatar"><img src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/d21a5a16465b1c74a5a4bf5cb09874af?s=75&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="75" height="75" alt="" class="avatar avatar-75wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-75 alignnone photo avatar-default" /></div><cite class="fn">Anna</cite><a class="comment-meta-time muted-small" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/03/lincubo-grottesco-di-cuore-di-cane-affascina-la-scala/#comment-16772"><time datetime="2013-04-04T11:34:35+00:00">4 aprile 2013 at 11:34</time></a> </header> <section class="comment-content comment"><p>Ho assistito all&#8217;ultima replica ieri e confermo: straordinario spettacolo!E&#8217; un po&#8217; seccante sentire il pubblico titubante dopo il primo atto, possibile mai che i milanesi abbiano sempre bisogno di essere convinti anzich lasciarsi andare all&#8217;ascolto senza preconcetti? Il lavoro  complesso, ricco, stratificato, spettacolare, frutto di collaborazioni tra artisti differenti che a mio parere in Italia si vedono raramente Bellissima recensione, restituisce e approfondisce il senso dell&#8217;opera.</p> </section><div class="reply clearfix"></div> </article></li></ol><div id="respond" class="comment-respond"><h3 id="reply-title" class="comment-reply-title">Lascia un commento <small><a rel="nofollow" id="cancel-comment-reply-link" href="/2013/03/lincubo-grottesco-di-cuore-di-cane-affascina-la-scala/#respond" style="display:none;">Annulla risposta</a></small></h3><form action="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-comments-post.php" method="post" id="commentform" class="comment-form"><p class="comment-notes"><span id="email-notes">Il tuo indirizzo email non sar pubblicato.</span> I campi obbligatori sono contrassegnati <span class="required">*</span></p><p class="comment-form-comment"><label for="comment">Commento</label><textarea id="comment" name="comment" cols="45" rows="8" maxlength="65525" aria-required="true" required="required"></textarea></p><p class="comment-form-author"><label for="author">Nome <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="author" name="author" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="245" aria-required=\'true\' required=\'required\' /></p><p class="comment-form-email"><label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label> <input id="email" name="email" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="100" aria-describedby="email-notes" aria-required=\'true\' required=\'required\' /></p><p class="comment-form-url"><label for="url">Sito web</label> <input id="url" name="url" type="text" value="" size="30" maxlength="200" /></p><p class="form-submit"><input name="submit" type="submit" id="submit" class="submit" value="Commento all&#039;articolo" /> <input type=\'hidden\' name=\'comment_post_ID\' value=\'49589\' id=\'comment_post_ID\' /> <input type=\'hidden\' name=\'comment_parent\' id=\'comment_parent\' value=\'0\' /></p><p style="display: none;"><input type="hidden" id="ak